The paper discusses a recommender system for research papers based on topic-modeling, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The system also takes user feedback into account, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and deep learning (cs.DL) techniques. Additionally, the system is designed for research papers, which could fall under the social and information sciences (cs.SI) sub-category.
